highlights.text: Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #9.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 134 weeks straight.
“Se Eu Te Perdoar - Ao Vivo” by Clayton & Romário and Zé Felipe is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #22.
“Camisola e Fio - Ao Vivo” by Diego & Victor Hugo and Lauana Prado is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 73 spots at #64.
